'''AN/TPS-72''' is a [[planar array]], [[E band (NATO)|E]]\[[F band (NATO)|F band]] air search [[radar]] based on [[AN/TPS-43]] and produced by [[Westinghouse Electric (1886)|Westinghouse]].

